.name
ColorReq
.author
Jeff Glatt and Jim Fiore 
.description
A color palette library callable from any program. Used to adjust the
colors of any screen. Automatically adjusts to screen size, number of
colors.  Has many features including SPREAD, COPY, UNDO, RGB, HSV, as well
as customizable gadgets.  
